2.15.1 标量对向量求导
\[
\frac{\partial f}{\partial \mathbf{x}} = \nabla_{\mathbf{x}} f = \begin{bmatrix} \frac{\partial f}{\partial x_1} \\ \vdots \\ \frac{\partial f}{\partial x_n} \end{bmatrix}
\]


2.15.2 常用公式







