2.15.3 标量对矩阵求导
\[
\frac{\partial f}{\partial W}_{ij} = \frac{\partial f}{\partial w_{ij}}
\]







函数 \(f\)
梯度 \(\frac{\partial f}{\partial W}\)




\(f = \text{tr}(AW)\)
